  <description>
    <p>
      WSelector is a modern GTK4/libadwaita application that allows users to browse and set wallpapers from Wallhaven.cc.
      It features a clean, responsive interface with support for searching, filtering, and previewing wallpapers before setting them.
    </p>
    <p>Key features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Browse high-quality wallpapers from Wallhaven.cc</li>
      <li>Search functionality with filters</li>
      <li>Smooth infinite scrolling for seamless browsing</li>
      <li>Filter by categories (General, Anime, People)</li>
      <li>Filter by purity (SFW, Sketchy)</li>
      <li>Auto resolution detection</li>
      <li>Drag-to-pan functionality in preview mode</li>
      <li>Support for multiple monitor setups</li>
      <li>Dark/Light theme support</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
